frames.caption: A large prehistoric marine reptile swims gracefully through a sunlit underwater landscape. The creature is surrounded by coral formations and smaller fish, creating a vibrant and dynamic scene. Sunbeams penetrate the water, illuminating the serene and ancient environment.
